The '90s are hot again.
OJ, Tonya Harding--

14:56.206 --> 14:58.586
- Right, the--the '90s
is also when most of

14:58.655 --> 15:01.758
Millennial's readers
were born.

15:01.827 --> 15:04.137
Uh, I have to jump
on a conference call,

15:04.206 --> 15:08.241
but, uh,
it has been a pleasure.

15:08.310 --> 15:11.413
♪ ♪

15:11.482 --> 15:12.896
- Ugh.

15:12.965 --> 15:13.931
- Don.

